reviews.review_text:
Classic 1990 Grateful Dead This was my first Dead show. I was 17. It was the first time I heard 1/2 step, blow away, let it grow, wharf rat, and the wheel. All around it's a great show and the end of an era as Brent died a couple of weeks later. After this show I was hooked.
 
Legend has it a guy had a sheet in his back pocket, it absorbed into his skin and when the cops found him the next day he thought he was a can of peaches, he didn't want water because it would dilute the peach juice and he would cease to exist.
